    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Creamy Bacon and Mushroom Pasta. A British home-cook's dish, the kind of recipe families adjust across generations. Adjustable for what you need.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Pasta in a pan, sauce in another. The trick is the meeting, the noodles finish in the sauce, holding the starchy water that binds the two.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
